            <h2 class="text-center">Refund Policy</h2>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h4 style="color: black; font-weight: bold; font-size: 25px" class="mt-4">1. Refund Process</h4>
                <p>
                    1.1 Refunds for cancellations of air tickets will be credited directly to the customer's wallet or the original mode of payment, as per the customer's request.<br>
                    1.2 Refunds will only be processed after Traveldealsonline.ae receives the refunded amount from the concerned Airlines, hotel, transporter, or other suppliers.
                </p>
                <h4 style="color: black; font-weight: bold; font-size: 25px" class="mt-4">2. Processing Timeline</h4>
                <p>
                    2.1 Once the refund amount is received from the supplier, Traveldealsonline.ae will process the refund within 72 hours.
                </p>
                <h4 style="color: black; font-weight: bold; font-size: 25px" class="mt-4">3. Mode of Refund</h4>
                <p>
                    3.1 All refunds will strictly be processed through the Original Mode of Payment used at the time of booking.<br>
                    3.2 No exceptions will be made to the mode of refund to ensure compliance with industry and financial regulations.
                </p>
                <h4 style="color: black; font-weight: bold; font-size: 25px" class="mt-4">4. General Terms</h4>
                <p>
                    4.1 The timelines for refunds are subject to the policies and processing time of the respective Airlines, hotels, transporters, or other suppliers.<br>
                    4.2 Customers are responsible for ensuring that all necessary documents or confirmations required for processing refunds are provided promptly.
                </p>
                <h4 style="color: black; font-weight: bold; font-size: 25px" class="mt-4">5. Contact Us</h4>
                <p>
                    For inquiries or assistance regarding refunds, please contact our support team at:<br>
                    Email: <a href="mailto:support@traveldealsonline.ae">support@traveldealsonline.ae</a><br>
                    Phone: +971 50 539 1369
                </p>
                <p>
                    This refund policy ensures transparency and trust while aligning with our commitment to customer satisfaction.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
